metadata.description: ANGELS v DEMONS is a new collection created by independent glitch artist sh4dow which recently caught attention in the web3 community with their release of glitch art collection "The V01D" (https://opensea.io/collection/the-v01d-by-sh4dow). Holding The V01D enables you to claim an AvD 1:1 for free, burn 1 The V01D for 3 free, or publicly mint. The public mint will only be open for 6666 seconds (1 hour 11 minutes) and the collection will reveal shortly after. There is over 100 hand drawn animated traits in AvD.
metadata.name: ANGELS vs DEMONS by sh4dow #1
